title: Tiesto Club Life 326 - 350
description:
My twelfth bundle for Tiesto's Club Life radio show.  I plan on seeding forever, unless I have a hardware crash or ISP issues, both of which are short-term situations.  I would appreciate other people helping to seed, and please be patient as my upload speed is not very fast.


The episodes were sourced from Raz0812, narrenpost, and kacper6711. Some episodes were from IndexTrance's split tracks, but I rejoined them back to a single file. Bundles tend to survive better than single torrents for each episode, so let's keep this one going forever!

I'm using the standard public trackers, and as always: DHT and PEX.
